<details class="audiobook-container">
  <summary>
    ▶️ ¿Prefieres escuchar la historia? Clic aquí para ver el Audiolibro Animado
  </summary>
  <div class="audiobook-body">
    <div class="speed-controls" style="margin-bottom:0.75rem;display:flex;gap:0.4rem;justify-content:center;">
      <button class="speed-btn" data-speed="0.75">0.75x</button>
      <button class="speed-btn active" data-speed="1">1x</button>
      <button class="speed-btn" data-speed="1.25">1.25x</button>
      <button class="speed-btn" data-speed="1.5">1.5x</button>
    </div>
    <video playsinline controls class="audiobook-video">
      <source src="{{ videoSrc }}" type="video/mp4">
      Tu navegador no soporta el elemento de video.
    </video>
    <div class="audiobook-download">
      <a href="{{ videoSrc }}" download="{{ downloadName }}" class="btn video-offline-btn" data-video-src="{{ videoSrc }}" data-video-name="{{ downloadName }}">⬇️ Descargar Video (MP4)</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</details>
